### 测试用例1：用户原始示例 - 返回NMX05

GET http://localhost:8080/api/mada1/qryMotor?speed=1&q=480&tl=18&wgtActualExtraDecoTotal=30

### 测试用例2：WGT超限 - 返回NMX07

GET http://localhost:8080/api/mada1/qryMotor?speed=1&q=480&tl=18&wgtActualExtraDecoTotal=60

### 测试用例3：Speed=3, Q=850 - 返回NMX20

GET http://localhost:8080/api/mada1/qryMotor?speed=3&q=850&tl=50&wgtActualExtraDecoTotal=700&wgtCarDecorationTotal=700

### 测试用例4：Speed=2.5, Q=550 - 返回NMX11-1150

GET http://localhost:8080/api/mada1/qryMotor?speed=2.5&q=550&tl=50&wgtActualExtraDecoTotal=300

### 测试用例5：无匹配规则 - 返回NA

GET http://localhost:8080/api/mada1/qryMotor?speed=3&q=350&tl=50&wgtActualExtraDecoTotal=500

### POST方式测试 - 返回NMX05

POST http://localhost:8080/api/mada1/qryMotor
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "speed": 1,
    "q": 480,
    "tl": 18,
    "wgtActualExtraDecoTotal": 30
}

### POST方式测试 - 返回NMX20

POST http://localhost:8080/api/mada1/qryMotor
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "speed": 3,
    "q": 850,
    "tl": 50,
    "wgtActualExtraDecoTotal": 700,
    "wgtCarDecorationTotal": 700
